#The red points are the probabilities given by Betway representing the probability of draw versus the probablity of home win minus away win.Blue points, are the real occurrences of those games. 
#For this analysis, the matches were ordered according to their probability of home win minus probability of away win Then,they were  grouped of 35 . Matches resulted draw for in each group were found.
#As it can be seen, distribution of  propabilistic values are more spreading than the real values. Thus, it creates a chance of making money from this difference.
#For real values above the trend line which are mostly accumulated between -0,1 and 0,25 , it can be said that  Betway underrated the draw probabilities. Thus, matches fall into those probability interval can be used to bet on to make money. 
#Also, it can be seen that Betway tried to adjust final odds (look at the left end of the line) It seems that Betway could estimated those changes successfully but made very small adjustments.
